The fork at https://github.com/hw1964/javalens-mcp extends the original
work with: multi-project workspace and workspace-scoped search (v1.3.0),
file-watch live workspace updates (v1.4.0), Tycho-aware Maven detection,
workspace bundle pool (Require-Bundle resolution), Gradle Tooling API
integration, parametric tool consolidation, and JDT-LTK refactoring
foundation (v1.5.0). See docs/release-notes/ for full history.

